@node _mkdir_r
@section @code{_mkdir_r}---Reentrant version of mkdir
@findex _mkdir_r
@strong{Synopsis}
@example
#include <reent.h>
int _mkdir_r(struct _reent *@var{ptr},
    const char *@var{path}, int @var{mode});

@end example
@strong{Description}@*
This is a reentrant version of @code{mkdir}.  It
takes a pointer to the global data block, which holds
@code{errno}.

@*
